window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>No communication. Limited power. An unbreakable will to survive.</b></p> <p>A violent blast of solar magnetic radiation plunges much of Earth into darkness. From the decaying orbit of the powerless ISS to a devolving Southeast Texas neighborhood and a secret doomsday bunker buried deep underneath the Colorado Rockies, <i>The SpaceMan Chronicles</i> tells the story of a stranded astronaut, his family and friends on the ground, and a shadowy conspiracy to rebuild the world in the shape of a new society.</p> <p>It's written with the help of former astronauts, NASA team members, and well-respected astrophysicists that give the trilogy a unique sense of detail and desperation.</p> <p>This bundle includes:</p> <p><b><i>Spaceman</i></b>: book one</p> <p><b><i>Descent</i></b>: book two</p> <p><b><i>Retrograde</i></b>: book three</p>"; 
